items.title: Stocks finish week higher; Wall Street at record highs
items.description: The Dow Jones Industrial Average rose 0.37% to 46,315.27, the S&P 500 advanced 0.49% to 6,664.36, and the Nasdaq Composite firmed 0.72% to 22,631.48. All three also hit record highs the day before.

items.title: Broader indices rally continues in third week; these small-caps rise up to 36%
items.description: The broader indices outperformed the main indices with BSE mid, small, largecap indices jumped between 1-2 percent.

items.title: Market extends gains in third straight week; rupee advances
items.description: During the week the Indian rupee traded in the range of 88.34-87.72, to close higher at 88.10 per dollar.
